text: Dominik Hrníčko (born October 29, 1995) is a Czech professional ice hockey player. He is currently playing for HC Bílí Tygři Liberec of the Czech Extraliga. Hrníčko made his Czech Extraliga debut playing with HC Bílí Tygři Liberec during the 2014-15 Czech Extraliga season. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:HC Bílí Tygři Liberec players Category:Czech ice hockey forwards
